{"tid":1706880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港非華語 we connect","createTime":"2019-11-11T07:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T08:01:44.000Z","uid":218990,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2b5b581d2f9b772321aa0b05b8e77412ce4738","tid":1706880,"uid":218990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"小女中學時讀國際學校<br />\n岩岩見到有啲非華語嘅朋友覺得燒人單野好過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我同佢講左幾句後發現佢哋咩都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n差不多200人被自殺<br />\n被捕後被性侵 等等<br />\n佢地全部都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以想問下咁多位有無英文頻道嘅ig page可以比佢地follow up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\nTg佢地唔多用 所以ig會比較好<br />\n<br />\n香港有好多好多嘅非華語 佢地對香港都好有歸屬感 我認為只要比佢地知多啲 一定可以connect到佢地<br />\n<br />\n最後咁多位手足辛苦了<br />\n我地一定要頂埋落去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"dd3e8c46bcb0469315078838e61f72da56b48df1","tid":1706880,"uid":218990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"2b34c008a145e10a666da1a98ad472e653d08356","tid":1706880,"uid":218990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"280bce2d17942cfc916780a30acf3ab5abd2e626","tid":1706880,"uid":218990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"f39937cff767e0e6c832128caf462b59176f3b4f","tid":1706880,"uid":218990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"0ae95a3ae412d9b795ad6e50dcad3cf1c55d2e94","tid":1706880,"uid":218990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:46:09.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"b353c8fb3fecb2921ce82c3f34f79e2e26db6aac","tid":1706880,"uid":218990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"光復香港"}]}